Package: ReliableChangeIndex
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Reliable Change Index (RCI)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Syeda Farah", "Zahir",, "s.zahir1@uq.edu.au", role=c("aut", "cre"), comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-2074-6999"))
Description: This package calculates Reliable Change Index (RCI) based on pre-test (baseline) scores, post test scores, pre and post-test standard deviations, test-retest reliability measure and practice effect (if available). This package implements methods described in:Hinton-Bayre AD, Kwapil KJ. Best practice approaches for evaluating significant change for individuals. Neuropsychological assessment in the age of evidence-based practice: Diagnostic and treatment evaluations. 2017 Jan 26:120-54
